body:
We want to be able to add the basic entities to the GraphQL schema. To be able to query, and mutate the things that are stored in the Catalog Service.

We should be able to get all entities from the Catalog, but also create queries to pass in typed filters too.

For this we need to model the entities (which could be considered the root elements) into GraphQL.

Could be something that looks like this:

```gql
type Entity {
    id: ID!
    kind: String!
    metadata: Metadata!
}

type Metadata {
    name: String!
    description: String
    namespace: String
}

type EntitiesQuery {
    all(): [Entity!]!
}

type Query {
    entities: EntityQuery
}
```

Which can then be queried like this:

```gql

{
    entities {
        all {
            id
        }
    }
}
```
